name: Meet the Wizard of Oz Pro
name_original: Meet the Wizard of Oz Pro
description:
All the Fun, None of the Ads.

Meet the Wizard of Oz – Down the Yellow Brick Road has 100 levels of pure fun. Connect wizard of oz images until you complete your mission. Think you got it, well new challenges keep coming up.

Features
– fun 100 Levels
– Connect Wizard of Oz Images to collect them
– Fun Missions you have to complete
– Use power ups like extra moves, live and bomb to help
– Play against friends in Game Center

Play Meet the Wizard of Oz – Down the Yellow Brick Road Today.
